## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The findings are limited to the sources accessed and may not reflect the most recent developments in communication technology. Additionally, the impact of technology on communication can vary widely across different cultures and demographics, which may not be fully captured in this report.